OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FSixteen and 17-year-olds will face a
OL,8,Fvoluntary overnight social media
OL,9,Fcurfew, the shut-down of infinite
OL,10,Fscrolling and breaks in AI chatbot use
OL,11,Funder plans announced by Technology
OL,12,FSecretary Liz Kendall.
OL,14,FThe changes, part of the government's
OL,15,Fwider restrictions on social media for
OL,16,Fchildren, will see default settings
OL,17,Fprevent access for older teenagers
OL,18,Fbetween midnightand6am.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FFeatures that keep users hooked, such
OL,8,Fas never-ending video reels and
OL,9,Falgorithmic feeds, will be
OL,10,Fautomatically turned off.
OL,12,FHowever, critics questioned the
OL,13,Feffectiveness of the measures given
OL,14,Fteenagers aged 16 and 17 will be able
OL,15,Fto switch off these default settings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's Government last
OL,8,Fmonth unveiled a social media ban for
OL,9,Funder-16s, which is expected to cover
OL,10,Fplatforms including Snapchat, TikTok,
OL,11,FYouTube, Instagram, Facebook and X but
OL,12,Fnot messaging services like WhatsApp
OL,13,Fand Signal, from next spring.
OL,15,FThe announcement came days before the
OL,16,FMakerfield by-election, but it will
OL,17,Ffall to contest winner and incoming
OL,18,Fprime minister Andy Burnham to figure
OL,19,Fout key details.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FKendall said the latest measures will
OL,8,Fhelp ensure under-18s accessing social
OL,9,Fmedia apps for the first time will not
OL,10,Fsuddenly be exposed to the most
OL,11,Faddictive features.
OL,13,FThe technology secretary said in a
OL,14,Fstatement: "Our consultation provided
OL,15,Fa clear message from parents and
OL,16,Fteenagers alike ` even as young people
OL,17,Fgain greater independence at 16, they
OL,18,Fshould still be protected from the
OL,19,Fmost addictive online features that
OL,20,Fcan have a harmful impact on their
OL,21,Fwellbeing.
OL,26,@vD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,F"These measures will be crucial in
OL,8,Fhelping young people get the sleep
OL,9,Fthey need, focus on school and
OL,10,Fcollege, and spend more quality time
OL,11,Fwith family and friends, all of which
OL,12,Fare fundamentaltobuilding a happy,
OL,13,Fhealthy and fulfilling adult life.
OL,15,F"We want young peopletoenjoy the
OL,16,Fbenefits of technology while having
OL,17,Fthetoolstomake the online world a
OL,18,Fplace where they can thrive."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FFamilies who took part in a government
OL,8,Fpilot involving more than 300
OL,9,Fteenagers and parents across the UK
OL,10,Freported that overnight curfews helped
OL,11,Fimprove sleep and concentration,
OL,12,Faccording to the Department for
OL,13,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,14,F(Dsit).
OL,16,FKendall also wants to introduce new
OL,17,Fsafeguards for children using
OL,18,Fartificial intelligence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FThe proposals include requiring under-
OL,8,F18s to take regular breaks while using
OL,9,Fchatbots, and a crackdown on AI
OL,10,Fservices that provide "dangerous,
OL,11,Fmisleading or unverified mental health
OL,12,Fadvice", with ministers considering
OL,13,Fbanning chatbots that pose a serious
OL,14,Fthreat to children, Dsit said.
OL,16,FNew guidance for children, parents and
OL,17,Fguardians on safe AI use will be
OL,18,Fpublished, and media literacy teaching
OL,19,Fwill be strengthened in schools from
OL,20,FSeptember.
OL,26,@rD@WOUtD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FConservative shadow education
OL,8,Fsecretary Laura Trott said: "This is
OL,9,Fanother dog's dinner from Labour.
OL,11,F"Either they think 16 and 17-year-olds
OL,12,Fshould be on social media or they
OL,13,Fdon't, but curfews they can simply
OL,14,Fswitch off won't achieve anything.
OL,16,F"Giving 16-year-olds the vote while
OL,17,Fputting them under a social media
OL,18,Fcurfew makes no sense.
OL,26,@pD@]OUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,F"They're also rolling out AI tutors in
OL,8,Fschools for the most disadvantaged
OL,9,Fwhile announcing more lessons on
OL,10,Fdealing with dangers of AI chatbots.
OL,12,F"They should stop tinkering and get on
OL,13,Fwith getting under-16s off social
OL,14,Fmedia."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
