PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FNSPCC chief executive Chris Sherwood
OL,8,Fsaid: "These proposed safety measures
OL,9,Ffor 16 and 17-year-olds will go some
OL,10,Fway to improving the experiences of
OL,11,Fyoung people on social media `
OL,12,Fparticularly having autoplay and
OL,13,Ffunctions that recommend content
OL,14,Fturned off by default and a curfew.
OL,16,F"But the proposals will not be enough
OL,17,Fon their own.
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,F"Unless they're followed up with
OL,8,Ffurther, stronger measures they will
OL,9,Fbe a sticking plaster that fails to
OL,10,Faddress the addictive design features
OL,11,Fwhich are driving high screentime and
OL,12,Fundermining children's wellbeing."
OL,14,FChildren's Commissioner for England
OL,15,FDame Rachel de Souza said: "We have to
OL,16,Flisten to young people. They don't
OL,17,Fwant a ban, but they do want to be
OL,18,Fprotected from addictive, infinite
OL,19,Fscrolling; dangerous strangers trying
OL,20,Fto chat to them and explicit content
OL,21,Fthey wished they hadn't seen.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@bO]wD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
