OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,F"I have called for action to protect
OL,8,Fchildren up to 18 and today's
OL,9,Fannouncement is a positive step. Young
OL,10,Fpeople tell me they try to cut down
OL,11,Fsocial media use but find it hard ` so
OL,12,Frestrictions on infinite-scrolling are
OL,13,Fwelcome.
