FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,F"I want to know more about how the
OL,8,Fpolicies, such as a curfew, will be
OL,9,Fdelivered and will be watching closely
OL,10,Fto make sure they are effective `
OL,11,Falongside pushing Ofcom to make full
OL,12,Fuse of its powers to make the online
OL,13,Fworld safer for children."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@ZO]
