FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,F"The Government has promised children
OL,8,Fa good childhood in the digital age.
OL,9,FThat means requiring safe and age-
OL,10,Fappropriate design across all the
OL,11,Fdigital products and services children
OL,12,Fuse, at home, school and everything in
OL,13,Fbetween."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
