CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,FAndy Lulham, chief operating officer
OL,8,Fat online safety provider Verifymy,
OL,9,Fsaid the default setting for the
OL,10,Fovernight limit for 16 and 17-year-
OL,11,Folds "will ask the most of platforms
OL,12,Ftechnically, since they'll now need to
OL,13,Fidentify and apply different rules to
OL,14,Fthree distinct groups ` the under-16s
OL,15,Fbeing banned from next spring, older
OL,16,Fadolescents, and adults with full,
OL,17,Fopen access".
OL,26,@sD@FOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
