OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784135918
OL,3,CTeenagers to face overnight social
OL,4,Cmedia curfew and infinite scrolling
OL,5,Cshut-down
OL,7,F"None of this will work without robust
OL,8,Fage assurance underpinning it. A
OL,9,Fdefault can only do its job if a
OL,10,Fplatform knows, reliably, that a user
OL,11,Fis 16 or 17," he added.
